title: Soldier
content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:SoldierThe RuneScape Classic Wiki also has an article on: classicrsw:Soldier

Soldier may refer to:

  • Kalphite Soldiers found in the Kalphite Lair
  • Sergeant Damien and his random event
  • Soldier found injured at the Death Plateau
  • Soldiers of the Yanille army
  • Soldiers of the Burthorpe Imperial Guard
  • Toy soldiers made in a player-owned house workshop
  • Vespine soldiers, offspring of Vespula

Shayzien[edit | edit source]

  • Soldier (Battlefront) found fighting in the Battlefront
  • Soldier (The Cloak and Stagger) found in The Cloak and Stagger
  • Soldier (Lizardman Canyon) found fighting lizardmen in Lizardman Canyon
  • Soldier (recruits) found training in the Shayzien Encampment
  • Soldier (Shayzien) found around the Shayzien Encampment
  • Soldier (tier 1) found at the Shayzien Combat Ring
  • Soldier (tier 2) found at the Shayzien Combat Ring
  • Soldier (tier 3) found at the Shayzien Combat Ring
  • Soldier (tier 4) found at the Shayzien Combat Ring
  • Soldier (tier 5) found at the Shayzien Combat Ring
  • Winter Soldiers found in the Wintertodt Camp
  • Wounded soldiers found at the Infirmary
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
